umer Domestic, Consumer International and", "bbox": [185.5, 686.4, 1024.5, 707.2]}, {"text": "Specialty Products Division (“SPD”). These segments are determined based on differences in the nature of", "bbox": [143.8, 711.4, 1035.0, 732.2]}, {"text": "products and organizational and ownership structures. The Company also has a Corporate segment.", "bbox": [143.8, 736.4, 973.8, 757.3]}, {"text": "Segment revenues are derived from the sale of the following products:", "bbox": [185.5, 786.4, 773.4, 807.3]}, {"text": "Segment", "bbox": [227.2, 831.1, 288.3, 847.8]}, {"text": "Products", "bbox": [456.2, 831.1, 520.1, 847.8]}, {"text": "Consumer Domestic", "bbox": [227.2, 861.5, 398.0, 882.3]}, {"text": "Household and personal care products", "bbox": [456.2, 861.5, 774.9, 882.3]}, {"text": "Consumer International", "bbox": [227.2, 899.0, 424.7, 919.8]}, {"text": "Primarily personal care products", "bbox": [456.2, 899.0, 728.2, 919.8]}, {"text": "Specialty Products", "bbox": [227.2, 936.5, 383.1, 957.3]}, {"text": "Specialty chemical products", "bbox": [456.2, 936.5, 691.6, 957.3]}, {"text": "The Corporate segment income consists of equity in earnings of affiliates. The Company had 50%", "bbox": [185.5, 986.5, 1005.9, 1007.3]}, {"text": "ownership interests in Armand Products Company (“Armand”) and The ArmaKleen Company (“ArmaKleen”) as", "bbox": [143.8, 1011.5, 1090.7, 1032.3]}, {"text": "of December 31, 2009. The Company’s 50% ownership interest in Esseco U.K. LLP (“Esseco”) was divested in", "bbox": [143.8, 1036.5, 1078.9, 1057.3]}, {"text": "the first quarter of 2008 as part of the sale of Brotherton. The Company’s equity in earnings of Armand and", "bbox": [143.8, 1061.5, 1042.5, 1082.4]}, {"text": "ArmaKleen for the years ended December 31, 2009 and December 31, 2008, and Esseco for the for the year", "bbox": [143.8, 1086.5, 1044.8, 1107.4]}, {"text": "ended December 31, 2007 and the two months ended February 29, 2008 (prior to the sale of Brotherton) is", "bbox": [143.8, 1111.5, 1032.9, 1132.4]}, {"text": "included in the Corporate segment.", "bbox": [143.8, 1136.5, 436.5, 1157.4]}, {"text": "Some of the subsidiaries that are included in the Consumer International segment manufacture and sell", "bbox": [185.5, 1186.6, 1043.8, 1207.4]}, {"text": "personal care products to the Consumer Domestic segment. These sales are eliminated from the Consumer", "bbox": [143.8, 1211.6, 1032.7, 1232.4]}, {"text": "International segment results set forth below.", "bbox": [143.8, 1236.6, 520.9, 1257.4]}, {"text": "79", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}